item.description:
After several Paranormal Investigations since our last evidence review (including a restaurant near Boston, MA and a residence in Southern Maine), I once again possess 20+ hours of video footage to view in preparation for reveals and to make room for upcoming investigations. I could certainly use the assistance from the lovely, multi-talented, detail-oriented and interested members of Seacoast Paranormal!

We'll be taking notes while watching video footage in real time on multiple DVRs. Be the first individuals to potentially witness & document real Paranormal Activity from several locations this Halloween!

I have reserved study room #1 on the 2nd floor near the photocopiers.
item.name: Halloween Paranormal Evidence Review Session
